# Blender authors level JSON; level/scene .blend files are never committed (principle #1).
# Exception: prefab/model ART sources under prefabs/ ARE committed (the editable source for
# the built glTF in app/public/assets). Autosave backups (*.blend1) are never committed.
*.blend
*.blend1
!prefabs/*.blend

